# Cline Assistant Rules

✅ MANDATORY PRE-TASK CHECKLIST:

1. FIRST STEP: Always read `context.md` file completely before starting ANY task
2. Review current rate limits, known issues and project state
3. Verify setup instructions if modifying scripts
4. Check latest commit history before making changes
5. Never commit .env file or API keys

✅ Always update context.md when:
- Rate limits change
- New issues are discovered
- Script behaviour is modified
- New features are added

This file is automatically loaded at the start of every session.